– 2nd level: May cast Monster Summoning I once per day. An additional use is gained at 4th level. 
– 6th level: May cast Monster Summoning II once per day. An additional use is gained at 8th level. 
– 10th level: May cast Monster Summoning III once per day.~ 
@112 = ~– Targets suffer a -2 penalty when making Saving Throws against Conjuration spells. 
– May cast the Monster Summoning spells as if they were one level lower.~

@113 = ~– Targets suffer a -2 penalty when making Saving Throws against Evocation spells.~ 
