@203 = ~ACID DRAGON DISCIPLE: Dragon Disciples are powerful Sorcerers with dragons' blood somewhere in their lineage. Their natural magical talents bring out their draconic heritage, allowing them to cast powerful magical spells and exhibit dragon-like abilities. Acid Dragon Disciples might trace their heritage back to a cruel Black Dragon, a treacherous Green Dragon, or a clever Copper Dragon. 

