@402 = ~Arcanist~ 
@403 = ~ARCANIST: The Arcanist combines the versatility of the Mage with the raw power of the Sorcerer. While many Sorcerers find themselves unable to learn magic from schools, Arcanists can adapt their own innate magical energy through careful study of arcane tomes and reflection upon the nature of magic. 

Advantages: 
– May change their known spells by expending arcane scrolls via the Arcane Versatility ability. 

Disadvantages:
– May cast one fewer spell per level per day. 
– Has a permanent -1 penalty to casting speed.~

