@21903  = ~ARCANIST: Some spellcasters seek the secrets of magic through intense study; others are born with magic in their blood. Arcanists seek to meld the science of wizardly scholars with the natural might of innate casters. An arcanist must prepare <PRO_HISHER> spells ahead of time, but unlike a wizard, <PRO_HISHER> spells are not expended when they are cast. Instead, <PRO_HESHE> can cast any spell that <PRO_HESHE> has prepared, consuming a spell slot of the appropriate level.

