  Damage: 1d10 poison per round
  Special: Slays creatures with 1-4 HD; creatures with 5-6 HD must save vs. Spell or die
  Range: 60 ft.
  Area of Effect: 20-ft. radius
  Duration: 1d4 turns

Requires:
 9 Intelligence

Weight: 1~

